                                                                <li>Processing an order*, including but not limited to:
                                                                    selecting
                                                                    carriers, establishing parcel
                                                                    dimensions, split parcel options, printing shipping
                                                                    label, etc.
                                                                </li>
                                                                <li>Managing and tracking orders, including but not limited
                                                                    to
                                                                    defining: order statuses,
                                                                    notifications and alerts, viewing order history,
                                                                    changing
